      599.71,
      524.48,
      663.49
    ],
    "text": "Investigations have been initiated by the Maradankadawala Police Station following a complaint received on the night of 07.04.2026 that a child had died after falling into a water-filled pit in the Kollakuttigama area within the Maradankadawala Police Division.",
    "fonts": [
